    {
      "name": "Explosion Release Clay Birds [A]",
      "type": "spell",
      "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Keywords: Hijutsu, Ninjutsu, Lightning Release, Earth Release, Fuinjutsu, Artistic Style</p><p>You mold clay, earth, or another inorganic earthen substance into three birds of your description. These birds then soar towards a target within range, ignoring cover. Make one ranged Ninjutsu attacks. On a hit you deal force damage equal to 3d10 + your Ninjutsu ability modifier. On a hit, affected creature(s) must make a Strength saving throw, being knocked prone and blinded until the end of their next turn on a failed save</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, the number of creatures you can target by +1 and the damage by 1d10.</p>",
